messageBody:
Hi All,

I have right now created an open group on the LinkedIn for the JUnit which we can enjoy.

You are All Welcome to join!

It is a good style that the professionals use in order to share their knowledge, code, asking questions, sending announcements, or even posting jobs, and discussing and clarifying detailed issues regarding the technologies -JUnit in our case.

http://www.linkedin.com/groups?home=&gid=4184979&trk=anet_ug_hm

With Best Regards,
Tibor
